To convert **3/4 foot** to **inches**, we use the fact that:

$$
1 \text{ foot} = 12 \text{ inches}
$$

So:

$$
\frac{3}{4} \text{ foot} = \frac{3}{4} \times 12 \text{ inches}
$$

$$
= \frac{36}{4} = 9 \text{ inches}
$$

### ✅ Final Answer: **9 inches**
